{"tid":2471961,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"加貓後friend過打band無碼實錄","createTime":"2021-04-02T04:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T07:22:27.000Z","uid":279122,"like":113,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc67ad066e47d5e304171a125f3fe460f372c95","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:11:59.000Z","msg":"差唔多一個月前 我就決定領養一隻新貓 原因係舊個隻肥到仆街想搵個朋友比佢一齊運動下 其次就係我男朋友成撚日同我爭貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />決定養多隻大家都有得抱！<br />\n<br />\n開po嘅原因係因為我前前後後用咗兩個幾禮拜先可以成功介紹到隻新貓正式入屋 一開始舊個隻見到佢就打 連性格都變埋 直情完全唔比人掂 個陣真係好灰好懷疑自己嘅決定<br />\n<br />\n係做左大量資料搜集同比左幾擔心機後 兩隻野終於friend到仆街 所以想開個po紀錄下我介紹兩隻野嘅流程 分享下比其他心思思想養多隻嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認得我兩隻貓嘅人唔好相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴番個頭盔 原諒我其實無影好多相 好多都係文字討論算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n介紹番 貓一號：肥野<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQYdZYhrf3SCJseTvyMjK4g17QHsAxu6BVK7SvpwZ9P8Y?filename=7qH2cRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qH2cRG.png&h=821fd917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年六歲 我係三年前 買餸經過見到有領養活動 轉眼之間就發現自己多左隻貓<br />\n<br />\n貓二號 ：豬扒<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRNrQpyqk3qgaaCePPKFGLp7oBLaahEEWx5zHns6QTgeD?filename=vVfy3ZH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVfy3ZH.jpg&h=32bc2a92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就嚟六個月大 一個月前領養 性格好撚癲 <br />\n<br />\n領養第一日<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeeT1bXVX2bW5bSNVtk86Nvh81Wdaf5WKB6yBp2AphXvd?filename=dQy5aFP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQy5aFP.png&h=4f1be83e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個日接佢番屋企 佢真係好細隻 回程個時係咁係到嗌 無錯 係好似被虐待咁嗌 番到屋企我隻貓其實第一下見到個貓袋唔係好明發生緊咩事 聽到有第二隻貓叫仲周圍係到搵 當我擺低個貓袋比佢聞下個時 佢已經開始哈氣 跟住驚到哩埋左<br />\n<br />\n咁我就帶豬扒入房 入面擺左貓沙盆同其他用品 佢跟住個幾個禮拜就會係呢間房到度過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRJNKZfNw3fZ6zpkyas5WzoFvGXtNNFvTn3bUNDQuw6VF?filename=4BZzOwm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BZzOwm.png&h=3dd4acc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備訓 聽日繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2a2e18eb352ca2e41bce9c807775c97f3ae67b","tid":2471961,"uid":8827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:13:32.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4ce3fff36aac1c9954047eefb9a49b08acfa7046","tid":2471961,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"早咗入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af85cdb0a4a382cd7ac478cb61ca590c4e443a8","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTKjme1j8uWSc7QwSXjEqMnxfXzVCFmoo4HKTGqxVrwV2?filename=dFxd39c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdFxd39c.png&h=3d4308d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補番張圖 證明佢地依家真係好sweet"},{"pid":"d2bbbce23439790699338759c64aac05d6015b6b","tid":2471961,"uid":128558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"男仔女仔？"},{"pid":"b5fa64618f4ff2f894cd9b7ef28e97dd828b8ef3","tid":2471961,"uid":385565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"你就好<br />\n我果兩隻仲係唔識咁"},{"pid":"8192e7e014dffa4fd13e686b521fbe35496f3cca","tid":2471961,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5af85cdb0a4a382cd7ac478cb61ca590c4e443a8","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dFxd39c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdFxd39c.png&h=3d4308d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補番張圖 證明佢地依家真係好sweet"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64343cbd1ef17d4fb7d6defe0db0c2fbb5d12da","tid":2471961,"uid":296582,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T06:28:27.000Z","msg":"肥野張相真係好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b455176b2d8416e4fc44527fb0d9938efd12be6","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d2bbbce23439790699338759c64aac05d6015b6b","tid":2471961,"uid":128558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"男仔女仔？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T12:32:05.000Z","msg":"兩隻都係男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02b34b83582e061d3f87088ee24c9954357e599","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b5fa64618f4ff2f894cd9b7ef28e97dd828b8ef3","tid":2471961,"uid":385565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"你就好<br />\n我果兩隻仲係唔識咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T12:34:54.000Z","msg":"我上網睇片嘅時候見到話想佢地接受番大家可以試下重新introduce番佢地兩個 即係當第一日好似佢地唔識咁 不過有啲貓其實係唔會做到朋友 好睇性格 所以只要佢地可以共同生活到已經好好架啦"},{"pid":"0872049fa25cb237bd0c7b4f910ed1e62d5c6b40","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64343cbd1ef17d4fb7d6defe0db0c2fbb5d12da","tid":2471961,"uid":296582,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T06:28:27.000Z","msg":"肥野張相真係好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"依家14磅 用左年幾時間幫佢減左兩磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a13b6f00485e7162b1b542882b57463930fceb","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"係領養之後嗰個禮拜其實情況都差唔多 咁我就group埋嚟講啦 係呢一個禮拜入面 我係無比過隻細貓出房 我上網睇到話一開始佢地其實連眼神接觸都唔應該有 因為貓係用氣味去分辨唔同人/貓 所以加貓嘅第一步 係令佢地熟悉對方嘅氣味！<br />\n<br />\n初期：<br />\n咁係講啲實際野之前 有介紹番肥野係咩性格 因為其實貓嘅唔同性格都會直接影響到加貓嘅過程！ 我自己嘅諗法係如果你隻貓係驚青/惡/比較老嘅 我會由隻貓嘅出發點嚟睇 因為如果你本身隻貓係接受唔到嘅話 新貓嘅壓力有機會造成健康/情緒/行為問題 貓其實係好廢嘅動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />壓力大會容易引起各樣健康問題 佢地亦會有機會開始隨地屙 所以建議考慮清楚你隻貓適唔適合有多個朋友 唔好只係因為你想要就攞多隻番嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdNeonGeEfE7XbcydLmM8hPhVAvU5tHmTDCm55n8gDQao?filename=eaeDyHK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeaeDyHK.png&h=3eb9feda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講番肥野 其實佢由一開始嚟到我屋企嘅時候已經係好痴人 仲記得我係領養活動見到佢 一抱起佢 佢已經係抓住我唔放 要個義工將佢係我身上捉佢落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 番屋企之後佢基本上來者不拒 有朋友嚟佢係會即刻去打招呼 係一隻好有自信嘅貓 而我播啲貓bb叫嘅片比佢睇 佢直頭會即刻開始煲水 所以我一開頭好確定佢一定會即刻同新貓friend到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後發現原來係我一相情願<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPFstwPZZRmZXWV5NyfCBEtnHTPT5zB1RuLSp8EUr7ZaT?filename=7ui5dJf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ui5dJf.png&h=2811a84d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8d8aee13f53b7b9d34be4b2ddc38f2e7bb0092a","tid":2471961,"uid":138482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10847a149c1e24c140275f53c54386327d9be6b","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQcZ5yPEa7tTc8xQKabck6XjB3kKp6QSGF4YK6S67oUkr?filename=N0Q3KRt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0Q3KRt.png&h=a1cac22b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始分開嘅時候 我等左兩日 見肥野直情係連豬扒間房附近嘅範圍都唔會行近 而我亦發現到佢開始連我地都驚埋 因為我地身上開始野到新貓陣味 所以唔比我地抱/摸 如果行近佢仲會哈氣同低吼 當我以為佢其實係咪憎左我地嘅時候 我上網睇原來隻貓唔係嬲 係驚 <br />\n<br />\n多數嘅舊貓係有新成員加入嘅時候 會覺得佢地侵入左自己嘅領土 驚起上嚟就會出現打或者跑嘅天性 睇個陣就梗係覺得好合理啦 但其實實際做起上嚟都咪話唔傷心 就連肥野第一日嚟我屋企嘅時候都未試過咁對我 但我係呢一刻 竟然要好似對住一隻完全唔識嘅貓咁 小心翼翼地比佢聞過隻手先決定摸唔摸佢 上圖就係個時嘅過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我嘅貼士係做好心理準備要瘋狂洗手 如果唔係 佢聞到你隻手有新貓嘅氣味可能會攻擊你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXnVQiexAMd7vh7oQGaHP8JyFQgJihTkYMp7wLKX3XLC9?filename=SbecDeQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbecDeQ.png&h=7c0846dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁係同一時間 我一路都係得閒就入房陪豬扒玩下 咁 注意時間要短啲 即係入去好多次 但每次都係留15-30分鐘咁 咁做可以避免舊貓妒忌 如果佢一發現隻新貓搶左主人嘅注意力 情況有可能會一發不可收拾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其次就係分房嘅時候要小心揀啲對舊貓唔太重要嘅地方 即係如果你隻貓長期係你間房同你訓嘅話 你嘅睡房對佢嚟講係好重要嘅地方 你一嚟就比新貓霸左佢最重要嘅地頭 咁佢就會覺得自己無曬地位同妒忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6a05155090a48e55d9c8d07f09c00464076ec3","tid":2471961,"uid":52088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"嚟緊加貓 留名學嘢"},{"pid":"953fe4599d7d74c9d56c4a51eba7714febed2c06","tid":2471961,"uid":367861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T18:43:20.000Z","msg":"Lm 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32471e156a43c76577b4f543f83beab38763f9c0","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T22:52:37.000Z","msg":"無乜人理我 咁我就自己繼續啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到大概第三四日 情況都無咩改善 所以我就決定加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下一步 我將佢地兩個嘅氣味交換 意思即係你求其搵張被又好搵隻佢地分別玩開嘅玩具又好 用件物件抹曬佢全身 重點著重係面呀pat pat呀個啲位 因為個到嘅氣味最勁 之後就交換兩件物件去對方間房 記住隔日就要幫樣野補一補味！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ9hkCdTwAWr79egpfP5FZYP1osdvVFKst3evHdCqMDRd?filename=99Wq1kX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99Wq1kX.png&h=05c4c049&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQEjav2SiDLiBuTMnFSuuADLhW8UZ2YZHJXt7vPQJsiyH?filename=GXhNveo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGXhNveo.png&h=11d6aed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁你會係圖到見到 我擺低隻襪之後 佢係完全無行埋去望都唔肯望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我最尾加多左好多其他野 實行迫佢點都要聞到豬扒陣除<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ1CKZxFW6LgtUCo568ZC12ezoDeJtoFjmtZG7EmwamTZ?filename=1MYXStO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MYXStO.png&h=8825cbfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就咁差唔多去到禮拜五嘅時候 我發現肥野終於開始好奇房入面究竟有咩 個下真係好大嘅進步 因為佢之前係會完全避開個邊 咁我見機不可失 就擺啲貓板/貓草係房門前 亦有乘機係個到餵啲零食比佢 咁做嘅用意係鼓勵佢行埋去 同埋等佢知到聞到呢陣味就等於係開心（零食）<br />\n<br />\n其間我都試過將肥野嘅正餐擺係間房前面 等佢可以聞住陣味開飯 不過佢個時戒心仲重唔太肯食 所以我都無迫佢啦 另外一個重點係 開飯嘅時候一定要餵左舊貓先！！！因為其實新貓嚟到 舊貓係需要建立地位 簡單嚟講 佢需要時間教隻新貓邊個係大佬 而作為主人係日常嘅生活上可以透過餵食/玩等等嘅行為 去幫助加快呢個過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSJGq5J7jt6fFCqFkadjXQ6pfHZizaHW2E1HYAQrjf6VQ?filename=RDG23D1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDG23D1.png&h=ee52dcba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"042c82539863ae41194b9160b3e0049fef6b5330","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":136,"dislike":0,"score":136,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T23:04:03.000Z","msg":"啱啱見佢地又勁sweet 有啲妒忌 補多張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYPPooq1XcFKb9jxtt8c69ZpKSm2Dq8sQEbbVaaaM4WzU?filename=ORfLg4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FORfLg4e.png&h=95081f33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10b884d028218d5d16b988f97553203046365bf3","tid":2471961,"uid":134438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T23:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae8752e97d81739ea98899de11b5035ccdc8cd6","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10b884d028218d5d16b988f97553203046365bf3","tid":2471961,"uid":134438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T23:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T23:11:13.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0cf0fd9725cc938838501860febef6c42806f3","tid":2471961,"uid":70834,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T23:30:17.000Z","msg":"繼續講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早排隻養左幾年既貓感冒幫佢隔離<br />\n另一隻老貓好似回春咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家放監，大家好似陌生人咁，包括我在內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0e60a4cf1aea11351ef946ca848588907d2551","tid":2471961,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T23:30:30.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續"},{"pid":"b2c7c7c2a2f31d4277db85ce6271ef5694c58b1a","tid":2471961,"uid":66488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T23:57:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f29d0a939269a30138e870e6a92a198acb1f1697","tid":2471961,"uid":251902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T00:14:57.000Z","msg":"我地都想加貓，但屋企隻貓對其他貓有d惡，<br />\n屋企得一房，諗緊如果領養到要點間開佢地..<br />\nLm學野"},{"pid":"53e1ba54882b44860618dab16705f90d292601e2","tid":2471961,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T00:16:33.000Z","msg":"留名一身貓"},{"pid":"78767648f47bd090146a085361cd8a4908e9acf3","tid":2471961,"uid":293838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T00:23:45.000Z","msg":"好正呀繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多圖pls"},{"pid":"e50773af1b5c126b4302a0957d753fa0a2fca141","tid":2471961,"uid":277843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T00:27:39.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心<br />\n我都留名學下野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429445d9b77bd918086bfb72648d8985681d0e5f","tid":2471961,"uid":57570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"係外國住？"},{"pid":"3f66489872e2319402fc011433f4bbed8c2c8963","tid":2471961,"uid":103146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T00:46:29.000Z","msg":"有貓我就推"},{"pid":"53a68f2cecf41825895583924b585571c808e1fa","tid":2471961,"uid":89285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T00:56:13.000Z","msg":"你就好<br />\n我加貓左半年舊貓仲係對新貓日屌夜屌，隔唔隔住都屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有壓力問題奶到個肚無毛"},{"pid":"8a32d56d21ced6d8b54f8e0587e54cfdbde070f9","tid":2471961,"uid":278569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T01:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c19a1cffacdf87298c9975cb9f29d4d24125d1","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5e0cf0fd9725cc938838501860febef6c42806f3","tid":2471961,"uid":70834,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T23:30:17.000Z","msg":"繼續講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早排隻養左幾年既貓感冒幫佢隔離<br />\n另一隻老貓好似回春咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家放監，大家好似陌生人咁，包括我在內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T01:11:34.000Z","msg":"有時啲貓病完或者睇完醫生 啲味有可能會唔同左 舊貓就會唔認得 呢條片有講解可以點幫佢地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DL3TDoSzsAI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDL3TDoSzsAI&d=oZ19EkYl1LXsHPE32KnJvbTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=3a7a894f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DL3TDoSzsAI</a>"},{"pid":"a5624e52e090ac9a64b825a3d946efefa9eab7d8","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f29d0a939269a30138e870e6a92a198acb1f1697","tid":2471961,"uid":251902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T00:14:57.000Z","msg":"我地都想加貓，但屋企隻貓對其他貓有d惡，<br />\n屋企得一房，諗緊如果領養到要點間開佢地..<br />\nLm學野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T01:13:38.000Z","msg":"貓籠或者廁所其實都ok架 籠嘅話就可以搵張被遮住 等兩隻都安心啲"},{"pid":"2d30c12096a3305f5d194bc96e2e213ddd9cb878","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53a68f2cecf41825895583924b585571c808e1fa","tid":2471961,"uid":89285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T00:56:13.000Z","msg":"你就好<br />\n我加貓左半年舊貓仲係對新貓日屌夜屌，隔唔隔住都屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有壓力問題奶到個肚無毛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"咁慘豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實可以試下重新開始介紹佢地兩個 當係第一日入屋咁 我上面po蘋果條片都有講解到點做 希望佢快啲好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38004611a26019a6440151f11465eeab9142901b","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"429445d9b77bd918086bfb72648d8985681d0e5f","tid":2471961,"uid":57570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"係外國住？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T01:17:42.000Z","msg":"係呀"},{"pid":"ee5223e51aa4a594a3fd12b9fe89a75f0b5fc10c","tid":2471961,"uid":160447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T01:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2隻都好可愛"},{"pid":"950638392b0d0b70874015f50a1923f5cf073756","tid":2471961,"uid":79427,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"樓主屋企幾大咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228cefc780a7293f40c50b99c8b833669af96d35","tid":2471961,"uid":108004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"我幾個禮拜前都加左貓<br />\n舊仔新女<br />\n<br />\n事前真係要做足準備<br />\n細既好活躍，大既好懶得郁<br />\n一靜一動岩岩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係未加貓之前都有幾次朋友寄宿貓貓過黎既經驗<br />\n所以對多左隻貓既警戒心可能會少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加貓前買籠(12蚊店砌)、舒緩香薰、滅蝨杜蟲"},{"pid":"c54bc587eccae1c0959c3705bdec55767a15c78d","tid":2471961,"uid":181321,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T04:15:23.000Z","msg":"你大鑊了，第一隻已經肥，第二隻仲要係黃貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8aac31cad13db730e767531c6a18df89360cc82","tid":2471961,"uid":76419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04