s/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3bac37d47774418f4a07616f2c5b74ae611f6d","tid":2471961,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T17:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01721471166ce86bc09d99e770f9d02d14683887","tid":2471961,"uid":104947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T02:35:44.000Z","msg":"我最近都加咗貓<br />\n舊貓 男仔 4-5歲<br />\n新貓 女仔 3-4歲<br />\n舊個隻好好，完全無唔開心表現，有時仲會去搵吓新個隻<br />\n但舊貓一靠近新貓，新個隻就fee同打舊貓<br />\n舊貓又脾氣好好，俾人打都唔還拖<br />\n<br />\n唔知點算，新個隻女幾時先可以唔惡舊貓啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50dab79606e63ffdc6c20bc3fc4ab520b22e5c0","tid":2471961,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"人都一樣<br />\n突然你老豆老母如果抱個陌生人返屋企同你一齊住<br />\n唔係咁容易接受"},{"pid":"8a034eaf333159636a6bbeb794c35bac9591fcd6","tid":2471961,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0872049fa25cb237bd0c7b4f910ed1e62d5c6b40","tid":2471961,"uid":279122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64343cbd1ef17d4fb7d6defe0db0c2fbb5d12da","tid":2471961,"uid":296582,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T06:28:27.000Z","msg":"肥野張相真係好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"依家14磅 用左年幾時間幫佢減左兩磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T06:29:11.000Z","msg":"兩年減兩磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73a5c881562a6f6e651481585dbc29a4c9a9a0c","tid":2471961,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"LM LEARNING"},{"pid":"0599554ceadcb1ee0b9573463c2f197069a1cda2","tid":24719