rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後發現原來係我一相情願<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ui5dJf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ui5dJf.png&h=2811a84d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T08:06:22.000Z","msg":"咩叫即刻煲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40689f1cad5db925cb1bf1a51e5d1ebd07065409","tid":2471961,"uid":135057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"Live咗，樓主更新未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184e7f96b540e467cddd2e9bf50747d46cc1a3c3","tid":2471961,"uid":79700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T18:28:13.000Z","msg":"樓主可以試下分段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 有文未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}